la.news-article238473004|department=Family Notices|title=Aronson&ndash;Baar|work=[[The Sydney Daily Telegraph]]|publication-place=Sydney|p=2|date=31 October 1882}}), after which ''The Sydney Morning Herald'' contradicts itself in a later edition and lists the marriage as being held on 23 October 1882 ({{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article13527109|department=Family Notices|work=[[The Sydney Morning Herald]]|publication-place=Sydney|title=Aaronson\u2013Barr|p=13|date=2 November 1882}})</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"baby-death\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article13544977|department=Family Notices|work=[[The Sydney Morning Herald]]|publication-place=Sydney|title=Deaths|date=19 September 1883|p=1}} & {{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article162027794|department=Family Notices|title=Births|work=[[The Sydney Mail and New South Wales Advertiser]]|publication-place=Sydney|p=572|date=22 September 1883}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"the-sun-zelina-macphail-daughter\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article231309976|title=Social Highlights|work=The Sun|publication-place=Sydney|date=28 June 1936|p=25}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"son-geni\">{{cite-web|website=[[geni.com]]|url=https://www.geni.com/people/Malcolm-Aronson/6000000057411003844|title=Malcolm Philip Aronson}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"thalia-on-miles-franklin\">{{cite news|url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.news-article183943496|title=Gossip for Women|author=\"Thalia\"|work=The Week|publication-place=Brisbane|date=26 September 1902|p=4}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"aronson-to-franklin\">{{citation|url=https://search.sl.nsw.gov.au/primo-explore/fulldisplay?docid=ADLIB110616021&context=L&vid=SLNSW&search_scope=MOH&tab=default_tab&lang=en_US|title= File 04: Miles Franklin General Correspondence, 1903&ndash;1953|work=Volume 9a: Correspondence with miscellaneous people, beginning between 1 Jan. 1903 and 17 Apr. 1904 and carried on in subsequent years|publisher=[[State Library of NSW]]|format=file|id=Call number: MLMSS 3